485
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:57,070
Saya akan menjaga
maruah keluarga Mo demi mak.

486
00:31:57,310 --> 00:31:58,000
Mo Fengyang.

487
00:31:58,950 --> 00:32:01,400
Mo Liancheng
hanya menurut arahan saya.

488
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:03,350
Awak memarahi dia.

489
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:05,560
Sebenarnya, awak sedang
memarahi saya. Betul?

490
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:07,830
Patik tak berani.

491
00:32:08,310 --> 00:32:09,680
Abang saya yang tak jaga kelakuan.

492
00:32:10,230 --> 00:32:11,760
Sebagai pembesar Dong Yue,

493
00:32:12,830 --> 00:32:15,160
