kad jemputan yang kolot.

545
00:34:23,230 --> 00:34:24,600
Mereka tak rasa segan?

546
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:27,150
Semua tuan muda bangsawan
menyukai puteri.

547
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:28,560
Kita tak dapat menghalau mereka.

548
00:34:35,950 --> 00:34:37,080
Menurut titah tuanku,

549
00:34:37,630 --> 00:34:40,280
